          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MAGSP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Elastic angular-dependent cross sections of",
                "Be-10,11 projectiles on proton and carbon nuclei were",
                "measured with spectrometer (SPEG) (see Nucl.Instr.",
                "  Meth. A276 (1989) 509-520).",
                "The good resolution of the SPEG spectrometer(delta-E/E=",
                " 10E-3) allowed to extract the elastic scattering data",
                "on C-12 without any contamination from scattering to",
                "the C-12 excited states.",
                "The scattered particles were identified at the focal",
                "plane by the energy loss measured in an ionisation",
                "chamber and the residual energy measured in a thick",
                "plastic scintillator."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "IOCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
